    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hellwalker: Gremory</strong> is a fast-paced action-survival roguelite where every run is a descent into chaos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight relentless waves of demons in a dark fantasy abyss, build powerful synergies through upgrades, artifacts, and class specializations, and push your limits as the world grows more hostile the longer you survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304670/extras/fa2f7ccf3344aa8c766c6e16cebc2bfa.poster.avif?t=1771603243\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304670/extras/fa2f7ccf3344aa8c766c6e16cebc2bfa.webm?t=1771603243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304670/extras/fa2f7ccf3344aa8c766c6e16cebc2bfa.mp4?t=1771603243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>BUILD VARIETY</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>75+ upgrades</strong> to customize every run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304670/extras/ddf711b19bc9a687d422bf09e1d31662.poster.avif?t=1771603243\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304670/extras/ddf711b19bc9a687d422bf09e1d31662.webm?t=1771603243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304670/extras/ddf711b19bc9a687d422bf09e1d31662.mp4?t=1771603243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i><strong>ARTIFACTS</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover <strong>20+ powerful artifacts</strong> that introduce set bonuses, unique synergies, risky trade-offs, and game changing effects that can completely redefine your build.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304670/extras/72f0cb8e194c923fdddb6e43879e8678.poster.avif?t=1771603243\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304670/extras/72f0cb8e194c923fdddb6e43879e8678.webm?t=1771603243\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304670/extras/72f0cb8e194c923fdddb6e43879e8678.mp4?t=1771603243\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i><strong>CHARACTERS</strong></i><br>Meet <strong>Shenra</strong>, <strong>Kaen</strong>, and three additional unlockable characters, each with unique playstyles and class paths.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304670/extras/b105a9190ac53126c2c90ee6d8eb8b4e.avif?t=1771603243\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304670/extras_big/b105a9190ac53126c2c90ee6d8eb8b4e.avif?t=1771603243 width=1560 height=868 /></span><i><strong>CLASSES</strong></i><br><strong>20 class specializations</strong> allow each character to evolve into distinct combat roles with unique mechanics and playstyles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304670/extras/655a00378588438143294da618188566.avif?t=1771603243\" width=844 height=504 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>EVENTS</strong></i><br>Face unpredictable events that force hard choices. Trade survival for power, sacrifice health for upgrades, and decide how much risk you’re willing to take to grow stronger.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304670/extras/d4da0feed68b3e83075b4620c40c9ea2.avif?t=1771603243\" width=940 height=662 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>ROADMAP</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Development is ongoing, with major updates planned after release.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• <strong>Online co-op</strong> (2 players) and Damage Leaderboard— Planned for a future update</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional content, balance updates, and quality-of-life improvements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >are planned post-launch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
